  <div class="col-sm-7 px-0">
    <h2 id="midd-story-label-modal-stories-alumni-01">
      <a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/sola-afghanistan-education-60-minutes-2023-02-26/">
        Daring to Educate Afghanistan&#8217;s Girls
      </a>
    </h2>
          <p class="f4">
        Shabana Basij-Rasikh &#8217;11
      </p>
              <p class="f4 mt-2">
        <em>60 Minutes</em>
      </p>
        <p class="f4 mb-3">A story of hope for those most in need. Meet Shabana Basij-Rasikh and the girls of SOLA.</p>
    <a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/sola-afghanistan-education-60-minutes-2023-02-26/" class="f2 font-medium story-link">Read more from <em>60 Minutes</em></a>
  </div>
</article>
