<div class="journey-modal__overlay swiper-slide story-slide" data-hash=slide7>
  <div class="container px-0 journey-modal__overlay-container">
    <div class="col-lg-10 m-auto mb-7 mb-md-8 mb-lg-9">
      <h2 class="journey-modal--title " id="midd-video-label-modal-stories-college-01">Middlebury College</h2>
                    <article class="journey-modal__story" aria-describedby="midd-video-label-modal-stories-college-01">
      <figure class="story__image">
              <img class="js-lazy-load" width="1136" height="639" data-src="https://www.middlebury.edu/sites/default/files/homepage/modal08/middlebury-college-1136x639.webp?fv=1" data-srcset="https://www.middlebury.edu/sites/default/files/homepage/modal08/middlebury-college-320x180.webp?fv=1 320w,https://www.middlebury.edu/sites/default/files/homepage/modal08/middlebury-college-736x414.webp?fv=1 736w,https://www.middlebury.edu/sites/default/files/homepage/modal08/middlebury-college-936x527.webp?fv=1 936w,https://www.middlebury.edu/sites/default/files/homepage/modal08/middlebury-college-1136x639.webp?fv=1 1136w" sizes="(max-width: 1136px) 100vw, 1136px" alt="A view from the college quad looking at the back of Old Chapel. Students walk along the path beneth trees that are turning colors in early Autumn.">
      
          </figure>
    <div class="story__content  m-auto">
                  <p>The cornerstone of the institution, the undergraduate College was founded in 1800 and is grounded in the liberal arts and sciences. From September until June, the Vermont campus is the exclusive domain of 2,600 undergraduates, who have more than 850 courses in 44 majors to choose from. With an 8:1 student-faculty ratio, the College is a close-knit, residential community, yet one with a global outlook; more than half the junior class chooses to study abroad. Middlebury College&#8217;s graduates go on to lead enriched and meaningful lives, with education, technology, financial services, and arts, media, and communications among the top career fields for recent grads.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.middlebury.edu/college/">Visit Middlebury College</a></p>
      
      </div>
</article>
